select M.*, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, income.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CASE WHEN M.NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY_COUNT from CP1UNCTMEMBER M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS income WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) and CP1.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR) AND income.index = 0 AND CP1.id = income.CP1GENERAL_PROFILE_ID

select D.*, CP2.DESIGNATION, CP2.ENTITY_YEAR, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY FROM CP2RCO_STAFF_MEMBER_DETAIL D, CP2COORDINATION_CAPACITY CP2, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 WHERE CP2.DESIGNATION = CP1.DESIGNATION AND CP2.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR AND CP2.ID = D.PARENT_ID AND CP2.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP2.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP2.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP2.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND CP2.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP2.ENTITY_YEAR)

select D.*, CP3.DESIGNATION, CP3.ENTITY_YEAR, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY FROM CP3JOINT_PROGRAMMES D, CP3COMMON_COUNTRY_PROGRAMMING CP3, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 WHERE CP3.DESIGNATION = CP1.DESIGNATION AND CP3.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR AND CP3.ID = D.PARENT_ID AND CP3.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP3.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP3.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP3.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND CP3.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP3.ENTITY_YEAR)

select BOS.*, CASE WHEN BOS.HASMOU = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as HASMOU_COUNT, CASE WHEN BOS.HASLTA = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as HASLTA_COUNT, CASE WHEN BOS.HASLTA = TRUE THEN CASE WHEN LTA.LTA_EVALUATED = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ELSE 0 END as LTA_EVALUATED_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CP4.DESIGNATION, CP4.ENTITY_YEAR, LTA.MONETARY_VOLUME, LTA.DISCOUNT_RATE_APPLIED, LTA.ANNUAL_VALUE_OF_TOTAL_PROCUREMENT, LTA.MANAGEMENT_MODALITY_ID from CP4BUSINESS_OPERATION_AREAS_DETAILS BOS, CP4COMMON_SERVICES_HARMONIZED_BUSINES_PRACTICES CP4, CP4LTADETAILS LTA, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 WHERE CP4.DESIGNATION = CP1.DESIGNATION AND CP4.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR AND LTA.PARENT_ID = BOS.ID AND BOS.PARENT_ID = CP4.ID AND CP4.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP4.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP4.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP4.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND CP4.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP4.ENTITY_YEAR)

select D.*, CP7.DESIGNATION, CP7.ENTITY_YEAR, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY FROM CP7MTDF D, CP7JOINT_FUNDING_PROFILE CP7, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 WHERE CP7.DESIGNATION = CP1.DESIGNATION AND CP7.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR AND CP7.ID = D.PARENT_ID AND CP7.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP7.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP7.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP7.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND CP7.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP7.ENTITY_YEAR)

select D.*, CP11.DESIGNATION, CP11.ENTITY_YEAR, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY from CP11DEVELOPMENT_EFFECTIVENESS_PROFILE CP11, CP11DIRECT_BUDGET_SUPPORT D, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 WHERE CP11.DESIGNATION = CP1.DESIGNATION AND CP11.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR AND CP11.ID = D.PARENT_ID AND CP11.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP11.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP11.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP11.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND CP11.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP11.ENTITY_YEAR)

select D.*, CP12.DESIGNATION, CP12.ENTITY_YEAR, CASE WHEN D.HAS_ENGAGED_DEVELOP_NATL_CAPACITY_TO_REPORT = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as HAS_ENGAGED_DEVELOP_NATL_CAPACITY_TO_REPORT_COUNT, CASE WHEN D.HAS_FACILITATED_FOLLOWUP_RECOMMENDATIONS = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as HAS_FACILITATED_FOLLOWUP_RECOMMENDATIONS_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY FROM CP12UNHRTREATY_BODY D, CP12HUMAN_RIGHTS_PROFILE CP12, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 WHERE CP12.DESIGNATION = CP1.DESIGNATION AND CP12.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR AND CP12.ID = D.PARENT_ID AND CP12.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP12.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP12.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP12.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND CP12.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP12.ENTITY_YEAR)

select D.*, CP12.DESIGNATION, CP12.ENTITY_YEAR, CASE WHEN D.UNCT_SUPPORTED = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as UNCT_SUPPORTED_COUNT, CASE WHEN D.HAS_FACILITATED_FOLLOWUP_RECOMMENDATIONS = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as HAS_FACILITATED_FOLLOWUP_RECOMMENDATIONS_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY FROM CP12VISIT_OF_SPECIAL_PROCEDUREHRC D, CP12HUMAN_RIGHTS_PROFILE CP12, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 WHERE CP12.DESIGNATION = CP1.DESIGNATION AND CP12.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR AND CP12.ID = D.PARENT_ID AND CP12.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP12.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP12.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP12.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND CP12.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP12.ENTITY_YEAR)

select D.*, CP13.DESIGNATION, CP13.ENTITY_YEAR, CASE WHEN D.HASUNCTDEVELOPED_MANAGEMENT_PLAN = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as HASUNCTDEVELOPED_MANAGEMENT_PLAN_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY FROM CP13SCORECARD_AREA_SCORE D, CP13GENDER_PROFILE CP13, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 WHERE CP13.DESIGNATION = CP1.DESIGNATION AND CP13.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR AND CP13.ID = D.PARENT_ID AND CP13.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED' AND CP13.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP13.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP13.DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND CP13.designation in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = CP13.ENTITY_YEAR)

select * from GLOBAL_CUBE WHERE GLOBAL_DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND GLOBAL_DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND GLOBAL_DESIGNATION in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = GLOBAL_ENTITY_YEAR)

SELECT WORKPLAN.ID as WORKPLAN_ID, WORKPLAN.DESIGNATION as WORKPLAN_DESIGNATION, WORKPLAN.ENTITY_YEAR as WORKPLAN_ENTITY_YEAR, WORKPLAN.WORKFLOW as WORKPLAN_WORKFLOW, WORKSTREAM.ID as WORKSTREAM_ID, WORKSTREAM.SECTION_ID WORKSTREAM_SECTION_ID, OUTPUTS.ID as OUTPUTS_ID, OUTPUTS.LEAD_UNIT_ID as OUTPUTS_LEAD_UNIT_ID, AGENCY_ROLES.LEAD_AGENCY_ID as AGENCY_ROLES_LEAD_AGENCY_ID, AGENCY_ROLES.ROLE_OF_PARTNERS as AGENCY_ROLES_ROLE_OF_PARTNERS, ACTIVITY.ID as ACTIVITY_ID, ACTIVITY.LEAD_UNIT_ID as ACTIVITY_LEAD_UNIT_ID, CASE WHEN ACTIVITY.SELECT_AS_GOOD_PRACTICE IS NULL THEN 'No' ELSE CASE WHEN ACTIVITY.SELECT_AS_GOOD_PRACTICE = FALSE THEN 'No' ELSE 'Yes' END END as ACTIVITY_SELECT_AS_GOOD_PRACTICE, BUDGET.ID as BUDGET_ID, BUDGET.TYPE_ID as BUDGET_TYPE_ID, BUDGET.REQUIRED_AMOUNT as BUDGET_EXPECTED, BUDGET.SPENT_AMOUNT as BUDGET_ACTUAL FROM WORKPLAN workplan LEFT OUTER JOIN WORKSTREAM workstream ON workstream.WORKPLAN_ID = workplan.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN OUTPUTS outputs ON outputs.WORKSTREAM_ID = workstream.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN AGENCY_ROLES agency_roles ON agency_roles.OUTPUT_ID = outputs.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN ACTIVITY activity ON activity.OUTPUT_ID = outputs.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN BUDGET budget ON budget.ACTIVITY_ID = activity.ID WHERE workplan.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND workplan.WORKFLOW = 'VALIDATED'
